data.text:
I got some Hyllus diardi jumping spiders, captive bred by me. Do not wait because they won't last long. They are too small to ship now and are local pick up only, Los Angeles area. No trades or price breaks unless you buying multiple. Pictured is male- dark and female- yellow.

CB Caribena versicolor slings $35 or we can work out deal with multiple.

CB Hogna madierana wolf spiders $20 or we can work out deal with multiple.

Roaches:

20 mixed Panchlora nivea “Giant” roaches, good starting colony.

Adults climb and can fly, nymphs need substrate to borrow. Easy to keep and great feeders for arboreal pets. $40

50 mixed dubia roaches $10

Isopods:

Zebra isopods $2 each

TOS: $100 minimum, payment is through Paypal or Venmo. Shipping overnight via Reptile Express. I ship Mon- Tuesday only and reserve the right to postpone the shipment if weather is too cold or hot in your area. LAG for two hours after delivery. Any DOA may require a picture and the cost of the animal alone will be refunded, not the shipping cost. jumpingspider
